Ionic is an open source mobile SDK for developing native and progressive web apps based on [Apache Cordova][] and AngularJS. The PSPDFKit PDF SDK supports integration with Ionic.

For more details, see the [iOS][ios ionic section] and [Android][android ionic section] Ionic sections of our Cordova wrappers.

